=======================
How to have media files
=======================

Quick instructions for Linux :
==============================

Run the getmedia.sh script.

Normal way :
============

1) Download the samples media archive :
  at http://objective3d.free.fr/release/Samples%20media/media.tar.gz in gzip
  or http://objective3d.free.fr/release/Samples%20media/media.zip in zip

If the link no longer works, check at the download section at http://objective3d.free.fr

2) Extract the content of the archive into the examples/media directory.

Enjoy!
